582
00:31:08,700 --> 00:31:09,800
Greetings,

583
00:31:10,620 --> 00:31:11,790
Your Majesty.

584
00:31:15,540 --> 00:31:16,540
Returning favors

585
00:31:17,100 --> 00:31:18,300
is a common practice.

586
00:31:19,420 --> 00:31:21,040
But is it worthwhile to

587
00:31:21,580 --> 00:31:23,540
take all the blame and die for

