00:32:02,740 --> 00:32:03,740
Then why did you

606
00:32:03,980 --> 00:32:05,180
commit those crimes?

607
00:32:14,340 --> 00:32:15,500
Actually, I'm here

608
00:32:16,460 --> 00:32:17,720
to tell you something.

609
00:32:19,940 --> 00:32:21,540
There's a fact you don't know

610
00:32:22,980 --> 00:32:24,510
about your father's case.

611
00:32:25,860 --> 00:32:27,500
15 years ago, your father Yan Changrong

612
00:32:27,500 --> 00:32:30,220
was bound to be executed
for delaying the delivery

613
00:32:30,220 --> 00:32:31,620
of an important message.

614
00:32:32,460 --> 00:32:34,050
He said that he fell asleep

615
00:32:34,100 --> 00:32:36,360
for unknown reasons and wasted half a day

616
00:32:36,700 --> 00:32:38,360
after reaching a postillion.

617
00:32:38,820 --> 00:32:39,750
The then Emperor

618
00:32:40,180 --> 00:32:42,180
ordered a thorough investigation.

619
00:32:42,540 --> 00:32:44,060
But before the truth came out,

620
00:32:44,060 --> 00:32:46,320
Yan Changrong hanged himself in prison.

621
00:32:47,500 --> 00:32:48,680
The coroner found out

622
