The case went into a dead end afterwards.

626
00:32:59,530 --> 00:33:01,260
The court had to drop it at last.

627
00:33:10,780 --> 00:33:11,860
Are Your Majesty

628
00:33:13,020 --> 00:33:14,820
saying that my father was set up

629
00:33:15,300 --> 00:33:16,730
and killed?

630
00:33:18,020 --> 00:33:19,620
Someone else intentionally

631
