caused the delay.

632
00:33:23,900 --> 00:33:24,860
Your father

633
00:33:25,820 --> 00:33:26,860
was just

634
00:33:26,860 --> 00:33:28,020
a scapegoat.

635
00:33:32,220 --> 00:33:34,140
Delaying the delivery of messages wouldn't

636
00:33:34,140 --> 00:33:35,500
do any good to the country!

637
00:33:35,500 --> 00:33:37,300
But it was closely related to the then

638
00:33:37,300 --> 00:33:38,760
military power struggle.

639
00:33:40,690 --> 00:33:43,420
Su Wenchun just became
a chancellor at that time.

640
00:33:43,700 --> 00:33:44,840
He had few aides,

641
00:33:45,980 --> 00:33:48,030
and no supporter in the army.

642
00:33:48,780 --> 00:33:50,260
After Prince of Mincong died,

643
00:33:50,260 --> 00:33:51,300
he tried every possible means

644
00:33:51,300 --> 00:33:53,100
to take control of Dingbei Army,

645
00:33:53,900 --> 00:33:55,410
but he failed in the end.

646
00:33:56,220 --> 00:33:57,220
Over these years,

647
00:33:57,740 --> 00:33:59,000
Prince of Dingbei and I

648
00:33:59,180 --> 00:34:01,040
have always found it suspicious.

649
00:34:01,300 --> 00:34:03,540
However, since we didn't have any proof,

650
00:34:03,540 --> 00:34:06,100
we couldn't do anything.

651
00:34:10,020 --> 00:34:12,350
Does Chancellor Su know about my origins?

652
00:34:26,460 --> 00:34:28,260
You've worked for him for years.

653
00:34:28,780 --> 00:34:29,420
Don't you

654
00:34:29,420 --> 00:34:30,699
know him best?

655
00:34:32,219 --> 00:34:34,060
There's no way he'd keep someone around

656
00:34:34,060 --> 00:34:36,120
and entrust him with important tasks

657
00:34:36,739 --> 00:34:37,820
before conducting

658
00:34:38,699 --> 00:34:40,360
a thorough background check.

659
00:34:41,980 --> 00:34:43,020
In my opinion,

660
00:34:43,900 --> 00:34:45,699
he must know about your origins.

661
00:34:46,659 --> 00:34:48,659
He deliberately recruited you,

662
00:34:49,699 --> 00:34:50,500
so you could

663
00:34:50,500 --> 00:34:51,540
be his scapegoat and die

664
00:34:51,540 --> 00:34:53,199
for him just like your father.

665
00:35:05,940 --> 00:35:07,060
At this point,

666
00:35:08,180 --> 00:35:10,240
do you still insist on defending him?

667
00:35:17,100 --> 00:35:18,740
I see him as my family.

668
00:35:21,100 --> 00:35:22,700
But he killed my real father.

669
00:35:25,260 --> 00:35:26,780
He gave me a new life.

670
00:35:30,780 --> 00:35:32,640
I can only repay him with my blood.

671
00:35:37,300 --> 00:35:38,490
I want to see him.

672
00:35:40,940 --> 00:35:41,800
Chancellor,

673
00:35:42,300 --> 00:35:43,430
it's all done.

674
00:35:55,860 --> 00:35:57,620
Do not take action

675
00:35:58,060 --> 00:35:59,720
unless it's necessary.

676
00:36:02,220 --> 00:36:02,780
Yes.

677
00:36:04,500 --> 00:36:07,260
What if the situation goes to the extreme?

678
00:36:10,010 --> 00:36:11,540
Then I'll take it as a signal

679
00:36:13,020 --> 00:36:14,460
from the universe.

680
00:36:16,020 --> 00:36:18,260
I'll do what destiny has planned for me.

681
00:36:18,460 --> 00:36:19,540
Success will

682
00:36:20,340 --> 00:36:21,340
await me.

683
00:36:21,460 --> 00:36:22,140
Got it.

684
00:36:25,140 --> 00:36:26,470
There's one more thing.

685
00:36:27,180 --> 00:36:28,820
A message came from prison.

686
00:36:29,460 --> 00:36:31,580
Liu Mo asked for a meeting with you.

687
00:36:41,060 --> 00:36:43,060
As long as he is convicted,

688
00:36:44,020 --> 00:36:47,980
I'll be safe and relieved.

689
00:36:48,740 --> 00:36:50,780
Plus, I won't have to make

690
00:36:51,580 --> 00:36:53,220
that risky move in the end.

691
00:36:55,940 --> 00:36:57,670
Go meet him on my behalf.

692
00:36:59,180 --> 00:37:00,820
He respects you.

693
00:37:01,860 --> 00:37:03,850
Try to persuade him

694
00:37:04,460 --> 00:37:08,060
not to cause any trouble.

695
00:37:10,060 --> 00:37:11,930
You haven't seen him for years.

696
00:37:12,580 --> 00:37:14,440
It's time for a proper farewell.

697
00:37:16,180 --> 00:37:18,580
Be with him for
the last moments of his life.

698
00:37:25,620 --> 00:37:26,440
Yes.

699
00:37:34,580 --> 00:37:35,860
Make it short.

700
00:37:53,500 --> 00:37:54,480
Mr. Si?

701
00:37:56,780 --> 00:37:57,710
Come here, kids.

702
00:37:57,930 --> 00:37:59,180
Come over here.

703
00:38:00,460 --> 00:38:01,500
You can have one.

704
00:38:01,580 --> 00:38:02,230
Thank you.

705
00:38:02,660 --> 00:38:04,220
-There's food for you.
-Thanks.

706
00:38:04,220 --> 00:38:04,860
Thank you.

707
00:38:05,340 --> 00:38:05,860
Alright.

708
00:38:05,860 --> 00:38:06,740
Share it, you three.

709
00:38:06,740 --> 00:38:07,460
Thank you.

710
00:38:07,460 --> 00:38:08,100
-Go.
-Thanks.

711
00:38:08,100 --> 00:38:08,860
Sit down.

712
00:38:10,300 --> 00:38:11,140
It's food. Come on.

713
00:38:11,140 --> 00:38:11,860
From now on,

714
00:38:11,860 --> 00:38:13,500
I'll bring you food every other day.

715
00:38:13,500 --> 00:38:14,900
Just focus on your study.

716
00:38:15,100 --> 00:38:16,580
If you get admitted to the academy,

717
00:38:16,580 --> 00:38:18,180
Chancellor Su will pay for

718
00:38:18,260 --> 00:38:19,780
all your expenses at school.

719
00:38:19,780 --> 00:38:21,980
Why is he treating me so well?

720
00:38:23,780 --> 00:38:24,660
Just now, you bravely

721
00:38:24,660 --> 00:38:26,060
argued with the officers

722
00:38:26,180 --> 00:38:27,660
who accused you of stealing.

723
00:38:27,660 --> 00:38:29,920
You defended yourself and your fellows.

724
00:38:30,140 --> 00:38:32,150
You even cited the law.

725
00:38:34,580 --> 00:38:36,860
Seeing the potential in you,
the chancellor decided

726
00:38:36,860 --> 00:38:37,990
to give you a chance.

727
00:38:38,220 --> 00:38:39,860
But how far you can go

728
00:38:39,860 --> 00:38:41,090
depends on yourself.

729
00:38:42,540 --> 00:38:44,800
I'm grateful for the chancellor's help.

730
00:39:01,700 --> 00:39:02,470
Pause.

731
00:39:03,140 --> 00:39:04,760
Point it up.

732
00:39:10,100 --> 00:39:11,600
Keep this token.

733
00:39:11,700 --> 00:39:13,260
If you're desperate for help,

734
00:39:13,260 --> 00:39:14,340
go to the chancellor's mansion

735
00:39:14,340 --> 00:39:15,540
and show this token.

736
00:39:16,500 --> 00:39:17,260
I just hope

737
00:39:17,940 --> 00:39:19,400
you'll never get to use it.

738
00:39:21,500 --> 00:39:22,680
Thank you, sir.

739
00:39:23,860 --> 00:39:24,740
Call me Mr. Su.

740
00:39:26,020 --> 00:39:26,860
Mr. Si?

741
00:39:29,060 --> 00:39:31,860
S-Shouldn't you be...

