00:39:33,220 --> 00:39:34,480
You thought I was dead.

743
00:39:37,980 --> 00:39:39,240
You're safe and sound.

744
00:39:39,570 --> 00:39:41,370
Why did you suddenly disappear?

745
00:39:41,540 --> 00:39:43,470
I haven't heard from you for years.

746
00:39:45,100 --> 00:39:46,430
I was ordered to lie low.

747
00:39:46,940 --> 00:39:48,740
It's water under the bridge now.

748
00:39:51,140 --> 00:39:52,900
Why would you resurface then?

749
00:39:57,500 --> 00:39:59,160
At the chancellor's request,

