757
00:40:43,390 --> 00:40:44,120
Don't worry.

758
00:40:44,780 --> 00:40:46,110
There's no poison in it.

759
00:40:50,100 --> 00:40:51,760
I've already pleaded guilty.

760
00:40:51,900 --> 00:40:54,760
The chancellor wouldn't
make an unnecessary move.

761
00:40:55,140 --> 00:40:56,260
If I die right now,

762
00:40:58,800 --> 00:41:00,200
