00:41:19,780 --> 00:41:21,780
became the chancellor's scapegoat

766
00:41:22,780 --> 00:41:24,380
and was at his mercy.

767
00:41:31,320 --> 00:41:33,140
Mr. Si, thank you so much for

768
00:41:33,180 --> 00:41:34,840
taking care of me 15 years ago,

769
00:41:35,780 --> 00:41:36,780
and for bidding me

770
00:41:36,780 --> 00:41:37,900
farewell today.

771
00:41:39,180 --> 00:41:39,940
You brought me

772
00:41:39,940 --> 00:41:41,540
the two most important meals

773
00:41:41,860 --> 00:41:43,180
in my life.

774
00:41:46,660 --> 00:41:48,060
I was asked to do all that.

775
00:41:48,900 --> 00:41:49,960
No need to thank me.

776
00:42:04,100 --> 00:42:05,100
I wonder what the chancellor

