00:42:21,700 --> 00:42:23,340
When were you chosen by him?

785
00:42:24,700 --> 00:42:26,500
Why would you work for him?

786
00:42:33,310 --> 00:42:34,530
15 years ago,

787
00:42:35,540 --> 00:42:38,400
I committed a capital offense
by deserting my post.

788
00:42:38,940 --> 00:42:41,340
The chancellor helped absolve me of blame.

789
00:42:41,500 --> 00:42:43,560
Thereafter, I concealed my identity

790
00:42:43,940 --> 00:42:45,540
and started working for him.

791
00:42:48,660 --> 00:42:50,100
Did you kill a scout

792
00:42:52,980 --> 00:42:55,180
named Yan Changrong 15 years ago?

793
00:43:00,460 --> 00:43:01,590
My guess is correct.

794
00:43:07,020 --> 00:43:08,700
Except me, all those

795
00:43:09,220 --> 00:43:09,980
involved in

796
00:43:09,980 --> 00:43:11,220
this matter died.

797
00:43:13,060 --> 00:43:15,260
How did you get to know the inside story?

798
00:43:20,500 --> 00:43:21,500
What on earth did

799
00:43:21,500 --> 00:43:22,380
Su Wenchun promise

800
00:43:22,380 --> 00:43:23,420
to give you?

801
00:43:25,020 --> 00:43:26,100
Why would you spend

802
00:43:26,100 --> 00:43:27,900
