808
00:43:44,020 --> 00:43:45,300
This is a one-way trip.

809
00:43:49,420 --> 00:43:50,620
You and I are the same.

810
00:43:51,780 --> 00:43:53,440
We do things against our will.

811
00:43:53,900 --> 00:43:55,300
